body:
Sorry to post on this old issue again; however, shouldn't the information about the ```fetches``` execution order being undefined be put higher up in the documentation? [Currently](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/Session#run), it is in the "Returns" subsection, but there is an "args" subsection which seems to make more sense (to me at least).

Should I open another issue for this?
